        "0.1.3": "<ul>\n<li>Prevent browser windows from moving\/blinking on initial click of anchor link. Props <a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/WebDevStudios\/Hash-Link-Scroll-Offset\/pull\/9\">@ImBigWill<\/a>.<\/li>\n<\/ul>",
